default21.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultManagement costs must be secured 
defaulti
defaultf the offset site is to stand any chance of avoiding a net-loss of biodiversity.
default A recent example from Scotland
default, involving a European protected site and Scottish Coal, highlights the dangers: Scottish Coal were g
defaultranted permission to mine,
default on the condition that 
defaultthey restore the site after use, only for Scottish coal to then declare
default bankrupt
defaultcy.
